Phenotype: Indicates type of activity observed: 0-10: Low Permeability; 10-40: Moderate Permeability; > 40: High Permeability.
Permeability: Permeability observed from the stirring double-sink PAMPA-BBB method. Calculations were performed using Pion Inc. software and were expressed in the units of 10^-6cm/s.
Analysis Comment: Annotation/notes on a particular compound's data or its analysis.
